<h1>About This Application</h1>

<h2>Data Sources</h2>
<p>This application utilizes data from the Dog CEO API, which provides various breeds of dogs along with their images and descriptions.</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>API Endpoint:</strong> <a href="https://dog.ceo/dog-api/">Dog CEO API</a></li>
  <li><strong>Data Provided:</strong> Information on breeds, sub-breeds, and random images.</li>
  <li><strong>Usage:</strong> The application retrieves data to display different breeds and their corresponding images.</li>
</ul>

